Title: You Might Be the Killer
Writer: Thomas P. Vitale, Brett Simmons, Covis Berzoyne, Chuck Wendig (created by), Sam Sykes (created by)
Actors: Fran Kranz, Alyson Hannigan, Brittany S. Hall, Jenna Harvey
Plot: A camp counselor suffering from blackouts finds himself surrounded by murder victims. He turns to his horror movie enthusiast friend for advice, and to contend with the idea he may be the killer.
